<div class="widget storyContent article widget-editable viziwyg-section-507 inpage-widget-8099115 TopArticleWidget" >
<h1 class="title">
Mullah Omar, creator of the Taliban, is dead.... for the fourth time
</h1>
</div>
<div class="widget storyContent article widget-editable viziwyg-section-507 inpage-widget-8099118 TopArticleWidget" >
<h3 class="subtitle">
<p>I was once told that intelligence services declare their enemies dead to provoke them into popping up their heads and revealing their location</p>
</h3>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="x940 topArticleDivider"
>
<div class="column-1">
</div>
